{"tid":874471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【習總南巡】「假食客」充撐場面 住戶忘閂窗被爆門","createTime":"2018-10-24T08:21:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T12:56:24.000Z","uid":75969,"like":139,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"76817178f032cf1a8d19ac8b8de4597a691539e7","tid":874471,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:21:30.000Z","msg":"中國國家主席習近平南巡，今早「駕臨」深圳龍華區龍悅居。由於龍悅居昨晚已開始戒嚴，居民出入均被嚴格限制，商戶亦要提早關門，以致全個屋苑仿如「死城」，當局今早已容許臨街的一些商舖及食肆恢復營業，並找了一批疑似警察、公務員或經「篩選」信得過的市民「扮演」客人充撐場面。<br />\n<br />\n今早10時許，龍悅居附近一處空地已有大批民眾被攔在塑膠「鐵馬」，遠遠的等待習近平「駕臨」。而在龍華區民治街道社區老人日間活動中心，今早亦有大批男女在場，疑是被當局安排到龍悅居扮「居民」，近距離迎接習近平。<br />\n<br />\n另外，當地警方以保安理由，要求附近的大廈必須關窗開窗簾，物業管理處人員在習近平「駕臨」前逐一排查，有些住戶離開時忘記關窗，有人被急召回家關窗；聯繫不到的住戶，物業管理處人員便請開鎖師傅破門，強行入屋關窗。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181024/large/1540347974_57b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181024%2Flarge%2F1540347974_57b0.jpg&h=883fe8a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">龍悅居部份臨街食肆今早恢復營業，食客疑是經當局「篩選」安排。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181024/large/1540348546_a10d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181024%2Flarge%2F1540348546_a10d.jpg&h=17acfcc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">不少民眾被攔住，遠遠的等待習近平的到臨。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181024/large/1540347974_e6a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181024%2Flarge%2F1540347974_e6a5.jpg&h=6e2e6c1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">大批男女在鄰近的老人日間活動中心等候，疑是被安排在屋苑內扮居民。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181024/58828851\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181024%2F58828851&d=pHDFri3JC9cxyroEx5P5vHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=b3ea7524\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181024%2F58828851&h=90a3e078\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181024/58828851</a>"},{"pid":"be432c878e582826c4afec159d7e530455ae9117","tid":874471,"uid":156652,"like":72,"dislike":12,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:22:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1jqKVhc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1jqKVhc.gif&h=794a0df1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d0c4a769cae1e46aa6852556a1d15112f6344e4","tid":874471,"uid":20658,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:22:51.000Z","msg":"笑撚死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8c15089309e0a0a4a6f4632db7d1a9f2a85f38","tid":874471,"uid":200595,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:23:28.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"0bb2e95b71f0774b1bbdd76e23ea913677418aaf","tid":874471,"uid":33099,"like":258,"dislike":1,"score":257,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:25:25.000Z","msg":"呢 d 咁既國家想做世界第一強國？<br />\n<br />\n人唔笑狗都吠啦"},{"pid":"6d72fe775ecb503a7b5b62d41062c93db9c5d156","tid":874471,"uid":20658,"like":6,"dislike":32,"score":-26,"quote":{"pid":"0bb2e95b71f0774b1bbdd76e23ea913677418aaf","tid":874471,"uid":33099,"like":258,"dislike":1,"score":257,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:25:25.000Z","msg":"呢 d 咁既國家想做世界第一強國？<br />\n<br />\n人唔笑狗都吠啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:28:43.000Z","msg":"唱首開始戀愛黎聽下先啦"},{"pid":"eaa819072edc9fe93fbc9b4309de7661fbe5e999","tid":874471,"uid":63154,"like":105,"dislike":0,"score":105,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:29:19.000Z","msg":"無撚聊，國家領導人有正經嘢唔做出黎玩role play"},{"pid":"e6e9d3269da76a761d8751ce32bc28f391f8b699","tid":874471,"uid":6111,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":1